WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Trapezik' is a Workbench game in which you create trapezoidal
patterns by rotating diagonal bars between surrounding borders.
When diagonal bars are placed correctly, coloured trapezes will
appear between those bars.

  That sounds simple, eh? To complicate matters a little, when you
rotate a diagonal bar, another one may change... can you create 52
trapezes (and 8 parallelograms) in the fewest moves possible?

  Have fun!

